name: Out of Nowhere (V)
Lore: 'Black market sensor-stealth arrays can be used to hide starships from enemy sensor scans. Stellar interference can naturally shield a starship for surprise attacks.',
Text: 'Use 2 Force to target a system or planet site. For remainder of turn you may deploy there even without presence or Force icons (Immune to Sense).  If you just deployed a non-Jedi character or starship to a location opponent occupies, take any one card from your Used Pile into hand; reshuffle.',
